Album: Coconut Oil (EP)Artiste: LizzoGenre: Hip hopRelease: 7th October, 2016Lizzo&rsquo;s EP, &lsquo;Coconut Oil&rsquo;, is an upbeat, fun-filled compilation of tracks that details positive vibe and womanhood. The six-track EP, a follow-up of her 2015 &lsquo;Big GRRRL, Small World&rsquo;, reinforces the idea of self love. Essential tracks on the album include Worship, Phone, Good As Hell and Coconut Oil. Lizzo is an amazing singer, spoken-word artiste and rapper, with a great voice and fantastic flow. Her work on this attempt is brilliant and certainly one to be admired.Star rating: 3 out of 5